        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="t1">T1</h2>
<hr>
<p>第一眼看到此题为树形结构，于是想到了树形DP。</p>
<p>看到要求:</p>
<ul>
<li>祖先在儿子前</li>
<li>同一父亲的儿子，要按照从左到右的顺序出现</li>
</ul>
<p>所以设 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 为以 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span></span></span></span> 为根的子树的方案数。</p>
<p>由于要儿子要按照从左到右的顺序，但在 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">DP</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span></span></span></span> 时不好处理。所以考虑倒序的形式。</p>
<p>对于一个新加的子树，首先他的根肯定是放在整个序列的首位（因为条件2），然后他的儿子没有与其他子树的限制条件，所以可以随便放（即插空），插孔的方案数为 <strong><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>C</mi><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{C_{L+siz-1}^{siz-1}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.216657em;vertical-align:-0.351862em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.864795em;"><span style="top:-2.406469em;margin-left:-0.07153em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">L</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.1031310000000003em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.351862em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong> （ <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">L</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">L</span></span></span></span> 为未加入新子树前的序列长度， <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>z</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">siz</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span></span></span></span> 为新加入子树的子树大小），然后用插空的方案数乘上新加入子树的方案数即为加入后的方案数。</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><munder><mo>∏</mo><mrow><mi>j</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">son</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></munder><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mi>j</mi></msub><mo>×</mo><msubsup><mi>C</mi><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>z</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msubsup></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f_i=\prod_{j \in \operatorname{son}(i)}{f_j\times C_{L+siz-1}^{siz-1}}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.5660100000000003em;vertical-align:-1.516005em;"></span><span class="mop op-limits"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.050005em;"><span style="top:-1.808995em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span><span class="mrel mtight">∈</span><span class="mop mtight"><span class="mord mathrm mtight">s</span><span class="mord mathrm mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathrm mtight">n</span></span><span class="mopen mtight">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mclose mtight">)</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.0500049999999996em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span><span class="mop op-symbol large-op">∏</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.516005em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.311664em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.286108em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.874664em;"><span style="top:-2.416338em;margin-left:-0.07153em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">L</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">s</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">z</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.341993em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>上菜</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">#include&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
#define int long long
#define mod 10007
inline int read()
{	int x=0;
	bool f=0;
	char c=getchar();
	while(!isdigit(c))f|=(c=='-'),c=getchar();
	while(isdigit(c))x=x*10+(c&amp;15),c=getchar();
	return f?-x:x;
}
using namespace std;
int T,n,siz[1005],dp[1005],jc[10005];
inline int ksm(int x,int y)
{	int res=1;
	while(y)
	{	if(y&amp;1)res=res*x%mod;
		x=x*x%mod;
		y&gt;&gt;=1;
	} 
	return res;
}
vector&lt;int&gt; Tr[1005];
inline int C(int s,int x)
{	return jc[x]*ksm(jc[x-s],mod-2)%mod*ksm(jc[s],mod-2)%mod;
}
void get_siz(int x)
{	siz[x]=1;
	int len=Tr[x].size();
	for(register int i=0;i&lt;len;++i)
	{	get_siz(Tr[x][i]);
		siz[x]+=siz[Tr[x][i]]; 
	}
	return ;
}
void DP(int x)
{	dp[x]=1;
	int len=Tr[x].size();
	if(len==0)return ;
	DP(Tr[x][len-1]);
	int now=dp[Tr[x][len-1]],sum=siz[Tr[x][len-1]];
	for(register int i=len-2;i&gt;=0;--i)
	{	int y=Tr[x][i];
		DP(y);
		now=now*dp[y]%mod*C(siz[y]-1,sum+siz[y]-1)%mod;
		sum+=siz[y];
	}
	dp[x]=dp[x]*now%mod;
	return ;
}
signed main()
{	freopen(&quot;t1.in&quot;,&quot;r&quot;,stdin);
	freopen(&quot;t1.out&quot;,&quot;w&quot;,stdout);
	T=read();
	jc[0]=1;
	for(register int i=1;i&lt;=10000;++i)jc[i]=jc[i-1]*i%mod;
	while(T--)
	{	n=read();
		for(register int i=1;i&lt;=n;++i)
		{	Tr[i].clear();
			int l=read();
			for(register int j=1;j&lt;=l;++j)
			{	int x=read();
				Tr[i].push_back(x);
			}
		}
		get_siz(1);
		DP(1);
		printf(&quot;%lld\n&quot;,dp[1]);
	}
	return 0;
}
</code></pre>
