<h2 id="t3">T3</h2>
<p>看到题面，手玩一下发现障碍的位置不影响方案数。</p>
<p>设 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>×</mo><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i\times i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.74285em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span></span></span></span> 的矩阵方案数。</p>
<p>考虑以下情况<br>
0 0 1 0 0<br>
1 0 0 0 0<br>
0 0 0 0 1<br>
0 0 0 1 0<br>
0 1 0 0 0</p>
<p>不妨设第一个放在第一位<br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="red"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{red}{0}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="color:red;"><span class="mord" style="color:red;">0</span></span></span></span></span> 0 1 0 0<br>
1 0 0 0 0<br>
0 0 0 0 1<br>
0 0 0 1 0<br>
0 1 0 0 0</p>
<p>则可以将情况转换为<br>
0 0 0 0<br>
0 0 0 1<br>
0 0 1 0<br>
1 0 0 0</p>
<p>这时候分为两种情况<br>
<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="green"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{green}{0}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="color:green;"><span class="mord" style="color:green;">0</span></span></span></span></span> 0 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="green"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{green}{0}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="color:green;"><span class="mord" style="color:green;">0</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="green"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{green}{0}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="color:green;"><span class="mord" style="color:green;">0</span></span></span></span></span><br>
0 0 0 1<br>
0 0 1 0<br>
1 0 0 0</p>
<p>此上情况为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f_{i-1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.902771em;vertical-align:-0.208331em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.311664em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.208331em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>0 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="green"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{green}{0}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord" style="color:green;"><span class="mord" style="color:green;">0</span></span></span></span></span> 0 0<br>
0 0 0 1<br>
0 0 1 0<br>
1 0 0 0</p>
<p>此上情况为 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f_{i-2}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.902771em;vertical-align:-0.208331em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.311664em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.208331em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>所以，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>×</mo><mo>(</mo><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f_i=(i-1)\times (f_{i-1}+f_{i-2})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.311664em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.208331em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.311664em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:-0.10764em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span><span class="mbin mtight">−</span><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.208331em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>上菜</strong></p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">#include&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
inline int read()
{	int x=0;
	bool f=0;
	char c=getchar();
	while(!isdigit(c))f|=(c=='-'),c=getchar();
	while(isdigit(c))x=x*10+(c&amp;15),c=getchar();
	return f?-x:x;
}
using namespace std;
int n;
vector&lt;int&gt; f[205];
vector&lt;int&gt; jh(vector&lt;int&gt; a,vector&lt;int&gt; b)
{	vector&lt;int&gt; c;
	int len=max(a.size(),b.size()),la=a.size(),lb=b.size();
	for(register int i=0;i&lt;len;++i)
	{	int shuz=0;
		if(i&lt;la)shuz+=a[i];
		if(i&lt;lb)shuz+=b[i];
		c.push_back(shuz);
	}
	for(register int i=0;i&lt;len;++i)
	{	if(c[i]&gt;=10)
		{	if(i&lt;len-1)c[i]-=10,c[i+1]+=1;
			else c[i]-=10,c.push_back(1);	
		}
	}
	return c;
}
signed main()
{	freopen(&quot;t3.in&quot;,&quot;r&quot;,stdin);
	freopen(&quot;t3.out&quot;,&quot;w&quot;,stdout);
	n=read();
	f[1].push_back(0);
	f[2].push_back(1);
	for(register int i=3;i&lt;=200;++i)
	{	for(register int j=1;j&lt;i;++j)
			f[i]=jh(f[i],f[i-1]);
		for(register int j=1;j&lt;i;++j)
			f[i]=jh(f[i],f[i-2]);
	}
	for(register int i=f[n].size()-1;i&gt;=0;--i)cout&lt;&lt;f[n][i];
	return 0;
}
